*Odeš* u školu svaki dan. (You go to school every day.)

*Odeš* li u grad sutra? (Are you going to town tomorrow?)

*Odahnuo* je kad je saznao da će *odeći*. (He sighed when he found out he was going to leave.)

*Odela* se i ode. (He got dressed and left.)

*Odoh* da posetim prijatelje. (I went to visit my friends.)

*Odoh* u trgovinu da kupim nove cipele. (I went to the store to buy new shoes.)